This log entry contains **two identical alerts** from the **Wazuh system**, triggered by **Suricata** on an agent running as `suricata-nids` (agent ID: 005). The alerts are related to a **potential exploit** associated with **CVE-2020-11899**, which involves a **multicast out-of-bound read**. The alerts are categorized under **IDS (Intrusion Detection System)** and **Suricata**, with a **severity level of 5** (which typically corresponds to **high severity** in Wazuh).
